race.comment: They'll go like the clappers in this. CARBONARA (10) got a well-deserved maiden win out of the way last time out and will have taken a bunch of confidence from that dominant victory. Winning rider Duric returns to the saddle and maps ideally for this from gate two. Can go back-to-back. WOOTTEN HYDE (5) has placed two of three over this track and trip and is yet to put in a poor one in six career efforts. Don't underestimate. READY FOR AIMEE (14) saves her best form for this six-furlong journey and looks one for the exotics players. ENFORCEABLE (7) best of the rest in a race with a stack of chances.
